snippet.title: Biolab Disaster
snippet.description:
Today I won't show you a DOS game, it's a small browser game instead. Biolab Disaster has been done by Dominic Szablewski in 2010. Originally intended to be just a demo of his JavaScript game engine called Impact, it became a fully playable platform game. It's entirely built on top of HTML5 and JavaScript, so there's no Flash involved.

You can try it there:
http://playbiolab.com
